title: Results of President Donald J. Trump’s Pro-Growth Agenda – The White House
content:
Fact Sheets			

		Economy & Jobs

June 5, 2018
The world is witnessing the resurgence of a strong and prosperous America.
						President Donald J. Trump					CRITICS DOUBT AMERICA’S ECONOMIC POTENTIAL: The Democrats and the Congressional Budget Office’s (CBO) somber predictions about the United States economy are not holding up under President Donald J. Trump.    DEFYING CRITICS: Under President Trump, the economy has come roaring back to life, with strong gross domestic product (GDP) growth, rising wages, and increasing investment.GOOD JOBS ARE BACK: In President Trump’s economy, good paying jobs are back and opportunities are plentiful.
